name: Ruins Key
flavor_text: Unlocks certain quests for 20 min. Can be used in Ruins Explorations (Home>Sub Quests>Daily). Can be purchased in Shops.

name: Attendance List
flavor_text: Unlocks Intensive Course - Advanced for 10 min, Intensive Course - Beginner for 3 min. (Until [1618361999] <tz>)

name: Boots Trial Challenge Ticket
flavor_text: Unlocks Boots Trial - Hard for 10 min, Boots Trial - Easy for 3 min. (Until [1625965199] <tz>)

name: Boots Trial Spree - Hard Challenge Ticket
flavor_text: Unlocks Boots Trial Spree - Hard, which gives 10x the rewards of Boots Trial - Hard, for 10 min. (Until [1625965199] <tz>)
